Edit:

- When you turn on the music on the button, whoever uses snd_restart will no longer be turned on.
- When you turn on the music on the button, it will not play or overlap.
- When you turn on the music on the button for other music, it will replace the previous one or start playing first, there will be no drawdowns fps will also not be included if the player used snd_restart.

I wish you success!
